WEBVTT

01:39.340 --> 01:43.479
[Road to Success]

01:44.700 --> 01:47.789
[Episode 4]

01:52.860 --> 01:55.990
[Will you coach the kids
to play football?]

01:54.310 --> 01:55.840
Good afternoon.

01:55.990 --> 01:58.530
[Not interested]

01:56.039 --> 01:58.280
Regarding my little proposal yesterday,

01:58.280 --> 02:00.590
could you reconsider it?

02:04.120 --> 02:05.200
No.

02:06.480 --> 02:08.150
So cruel.

02:23.400 --> 02:26.270
Every time he appeared, he acted weird

02:26.290 --> 02:27.890
and had unclear intentions.

02:28.700 --> 02:30.840
What kind of person is he?

02:39.540 --> 02:40.430
Ms. Lin.

02:40.450 --> 02:41.079
Ms. Lin.

02:41.110 --> 02:41.790
Ms. Lin.

02:44.120 --> 02:45.430
Do you need something?

02:46.800 --> 02:48.960
W-We just wanted to ask you

02:49.470 --> 02:50.310
if Coach Wang Fa

02:50.310 --> 02:51.710
agreed to be our coach.

02:52.840 --> 02:53.770
[Winfred]

02:53.800 --> 02:53.990
[School Sports Equipment Room Work Plan]

02:57.070 --> 02:57.860
Ask him.

02:59.360 --> 03:01.020
He didn't just refuse, did he?

03:01.560 --> 03:03.120
-Not—
-Ms. Lin.

03:03.630 --> 03:05.150
You are not brushing us off, are you?

03:05.150 --> 03:07.280
You didn't do anything at all, did you?

03:09.290 --> 03:11.320
How could you wrong me like this?

03:11.800 --> 03:13.910
I am working so hard to find you a coach,

03:13.910 --> 03:15.910
and you say I'm brushing you off.

03:15.910 --> 03:16.690
So,

03:16.720 --> 03:17.880
did he refuse?

03:19.970 --> 03:21.079
Not completely.

03:21.650 --> 03:23.380
That means there is still hope.

03:26.270 --> 03:27.620
I will do my best.

03:27.640 --> 03:29.100
Do you need anything else?

03:29.240 --> 03:30.240
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

03:30.240 --> 03:30.870
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

03:30.870 --> 03:31.590
Goodbye, Ms. Lin.

03:31.590 --> 03:32.590
Bye-bye, Ms. Lin.

03:34.880 --> 03:36.340
My football lending card.

03:36.760 --> 03:37.700
Ms. Lin,

03:38.160 --> 03:39.350
use your charm.

03:47.150 --> 03:48.750
I need to think of a good way

03:48.750 --> 03:50.310
to deal with him.

03:52.400 --> 03:53.750
Come on.

04:08.680 --> 04:09.190
You know what?

04:09.190 --> 04:11.390
I missed this so much
when I was in the UK.

04:13.080 --> 04:14.590
Didn't the team hire a Chinese chef?

04:14.590 --> 04:15.310
Don't mention him.

04:15.310 --> 04:16.589
He's from Wuxi.

04:16.910 --> 04:18.430
He adds sugar to everything.

04:18.430 --> 04:20.959
Only your favorite student
likes sweet food.

04:22.120 --> 04:23.680
As a result, I had to control
his body fat

04:23.680 --> 04:26.140
and strictly forbid him
from eating sweets.

04:27.230 --> 04:28.230
Sorry about that.

04:29.540 --> 04:30.580
By the way,

04:30.600 --> 04:33.260
any clues on your investigation
of Lin Wanxing?

04:34.190 --> 04:35.040
Not yet.

04:35.230 --> 04:36.400
But I have a plan.

04:38.200 --> 04:39.659
W-What are you going to do?

04:41.760 --> 04:43.600
The floor in my place has water seepage.

04:43.600 --> 04:45.200
I can seize the chance to go to her place

04:45.200 --> 04:46.530
and check her computer.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.630
Go to her place?

04:48.659 --> 04:49.920
A man and a woman alone?

04:49.930 --> 04:51.200
Are you into her?

04:51.720 --> 04:53.159
Can you be serious?

04:56.820 --> 04:58.200
Okay. I'm familiar with this.

04:58.200 --> 04:59.310
Let me teach you.

04:59.310 --> 05:00.670
After you go there,

05:01.230 --> 05:02.360
break her computer.

05:03.560 --> 05:05.420
Back up all files while fixing it.

05:05.870 --> 05:06.360
Perfect.

05:06.360 --> 05:07.040
How is it?

05:07.480 --> 05:09.360
Last time you came up
with a bad idea like this,

05:09.360 --> 05:11.210
you broke my sister's stereo
and took it for repair.

05:11.210 --> 05:13.440
Didn't you almost electrocute yourself?

05:13.440 --> 05:14.230
Well...

05:19.830 --> 05:20.480
Shut up.

05:21.040 --> 05:21.430
Let's drop it.

05:21.430 --> 05:23.430
Change the topic and eat the shrimp.

05:23.680 --> 05:24.770
You are my brother-in-law.

05:24.770 --> 05:25.570
Peel it for me.

05:27.190 --> 05:29.160
Why are you so impolite?

05:29.800 --> 05:30.680
Are you sure

05:30.680 --> 05:32.240
she will invite you to her place?

05:32.240 --> 05:33.070
Probably.

05:34.590 --> 05:35.820
Do you mean

05:35.850 --> 05:37.450
I can't stay at home tonight?

05:37.909 --> 05:38.840
Right, Mr. Wang.

05:39.010 --> 05:41.000
This old house has terrible waterproofing,

05:41.000 --> 05:42.870
so we'll have to apply two coats.

05:42.980 --> 05:45.010
To finish it as soon as possible tomorrow,

05:45.010 --> 05:45.840
we have to work

05:45.860 --> 05:46.710
late tonight.

05:47.490 --> 05:48.490
Okay. No problem.

05:49.110 --> 05:50.260
I can stay in a hotel.

05:50.850 --> 05:51.440
Okay.

05:56.480 --> 05:58.430
He has to stay in a hotel tonight.

05:58.430 --> 05:59.430
Thanks for your hard work.

05:59.430 --> 06:00.090
No problem.

06:02.250 --> 06:04.250
Congratulations. Great progress.

06:04.510 --> 06:05.350
Almost done.

06:05.690 --> 06:06.640
I can tell.

06:10.360 --> 06:11.190
What's up?

06:13.240 --> 06:14.730
I wonder if you agree

06:14.860 --> 06:16.580
to coach the football team.

06:16.610 --> 06:17.890
I told you

06:17.910 --> 06:18.560
I'm not interested.

06:18.560 --> 06:20.180
Don't be in a rush to refuse.

06:20.210 --> 06:22.370
Aren't you curious about the pay first?

06:22.370 --> 06:23.490
Name your price.

06:23.720 --> 06:24.480
Sorry.

06:25.230 --> 06:26.430
You can't afford me.

06:27.270 --> 06:29.070
So pretentious.

06:29.390 --> 06:30.390
I'll bear with it.

06:30.800 --> 06:32.170
I'll waive your rent.

06:32.430 --> 06:34.730
I'll waive it as long as you coach them.

06:34.750 --> 06:36.360
I don't need it.

06:36.700 --> 06:38.170
So arrogant.

06:38.200 --> 06:40.460
Do you know how much it costs

06:40.490 --> 06:41.390
to maintain a football team?

06:41.390 --> 06:43.230
Isn't it still about money?

06:43.470 --> 06:44.470
I'm not sure.

06:44.970 --> 06:46.170
But I guess

06:46.240 --> 06:47.120
most of the expenses

06:47.120 --> 06:49.020
go toward the coach's salary.

06:49.110 --> 06:50.790
Don't waste your time on me.

06:50.810 --> 06:51.950
Find someone else.

06:51.970 --> 06:53.530
So stubborn.

06:53.560 --> 06:54.159
Sir.

06:54.470 --> 06:55.900
Please apply more waterproof coating

06:55.900 --> 06:56.950
on this side for me.

06:56.950 --> 06:57.740
Okay.

06:57.760 --> 06:59.920
Then don't blame me.

06:59.940 --> 07:01.670
I'll take your ID card.

07:01.700 --> 07:03.360
Let's see how you check into a hotel.

07:03.360 --> 07:04.360
Go ahead then.

07:04.360 --> 07:05.750
I won't bother you.

07:07.820 --> 07:09.710
We're doing it very carefully.

07:13.370 --> 07:14.590
[Name: Wang Fa]

07:14.670 --> 07:17.970
[Resident Identity Card
of the People's Republic of China]

07:18.790 --> 07:20.620
To be honest,

07:20.640 --> 07:22.750
Mr. Win's flat 2D portrait

07:22.830 --> 07:24.800
is quite pleasing to the eye.

07:26.070 --> 07:27.870
It's definitely photoshopped.

07:27.880 --> 07:29.620
Once he starts to speak,

07:29.640 --> 07:31.740
he gradually becomes repulsive.

07:36.710 --> 07:38.950
I don't believe I can't win you over.

07:38.600 --> 07:39.470
[Winfred Wang] [Search]

07:41.090 --> 07:43.450
[Winfred Wang]

07:46.110 --> 07:49.500
[Notes]

07:50.010 --> 07:51.120
Cold.

07:51.470 --> 07:52.550
Aloof.

07:53.040 --> 07:54.240
Autistic.

07:57.310 --> 08:00.240
And with typical
obsessive-compulsive behaviors.

08:02.800 --> 08:05.270
He's more than just hard to deal with.

08:05.680 --> 08:07.480
Extremely hard.

08:09.100 --> 08:11.260
[Fragment] [Fall]

08:19.480 --> 08:20.680
Mr. Win,

08:20.680 --> 08:24.070
it's time to show you my professionalism.

08:26.190 --> 08:27.600
But...

08:28.070 --> 08:30.710
he's quite an interesting person.

08:30.740 --> 08:32.179
Rational,

08:32.200 --> 08:33.640
disciplined,

08:33.870 --> 08:35.320
visionary,

08:35.549 --> 08:38.120
and with an extraordinary understanding
of football.

08:37.950 --> 08:42.000
[Tendency-Oriented Methodology
for Rectifying Wang Fa's Conduct]

08:38.590 --> 08:39.350
No.

08:39.370 --> 08:41.039
Why am I praising him?

08:45.510 --> 08:47.150
Tendency-Oriented Methodology

08:47.150 --> 08:49.390
for Rectifying Wang Fa's Conduct.

08:49.440 --> 08:51.990
Let's start with the foot-in-the-door
and suspension bridge effects.

08:49.540 --> 08:51.150
[Make a Strategic Plan]

08:51.150 --> 08:54.750
[Strategic Plan]
[Suspension bridge effect]

08:53.120 --> 08:53.930
To deal with an ordinary person,

08:53.930 --> 08:55.570
these two are enough.

08:55.240 --> 08:56.820
[Foot-in-the-door effect]

08:56.390 --> 08:58.960
Given that he's extremely
hard to deal with,

08:57.200 --> 08:59.090
[Door-in-the-face effect]

08:58.960 --> 09:01.510
add the door-in-the-face effect.

08:59.160 --> 09:00.820
[Suspension bridge effect: Build
tense atmosphere to boost adrenaline]

09:00.840 --> 09:03.360
[Foot-in-the-door effect: Break ice
via physical touch & define core needs]

09:02.720 --> 09:04.750
With such a detailed strategic plan,

09:03.390 --> 09:06.090
[Door-in-the-face effect:
Excessive requests, fallback demands]

09:04.750 --> 09:07.080
I don't believe I can't win you over.

09:09.390 --> 09:11.100
[Make a Strategic Plan]

09:12.870 --> 09:14.630
Strategy No. 1,

09:14.650 --> 09:16.490
the foot-in-the-door effect.

09:16.630 --> 09:18.360
Ask for his help appropriately.

09:18.360 --> 09:20.530
It can make him like me more.

09:20.550 --> 09:21.980
Because after helping me,

09:21.980 --> 09:23.990
he'll adjust his feelings toward me

09:24.020 --> 09:26.380
and think I'm someone worth helping.

09:32.960 --> 09:34.270
Why is it crooked?

09:38.240 --> 09:39.200
Let me help you.

09:40.070 --> 09:41.160
It really works.

09:41.180 --> 09:42.120
Leave this kind of thing

09:42.120 --> 09:42.880
to me.

09:45.360 --> 09:47.490
Being tall really has its advantages.

09:48.870 --> 09:49.840
A piece of cake.

09:50.110 --> 09:51.370
Nailed it.

09:51.670 --> 09:53.080
[Make a Strategic Plan]

09:53.530 --> 09:55.740
Strategy No. 2,

09:55.910 --> 09:57.630
the suspension bridge effect.

09:57.630 --> 10:00.200
When a person is in a dangerous situation,

10:00.200 --> 10:02.510
like on a suspension bridge,

10:02.530 --> 10:04.690
if he meets another person,

10:04.720 --> 10:07.370
he'll naturally develop
trust and reliance.

10:07.870 --> 10:08.870
Here it comes.

10:09.510 --> 10:11.890
The scariest part is coming.

10:12.870 --> 10:14.840
It's my turn.

10:31.390 --> 10:32.320
Who is it?

10:33.030 --> 10:33.790
It's me.

10:37.240 --> 10:38.210
Coming.

10:43.270 --> 10:44.150
What's up?

10:46.060 --> 10:47.230
I lost my ID card.

10:47.270 --> 10:48.080
I wanted to ask

10:48.080 --> 10:50.480
where I can get a temporary one
around here.

10:50.520 --> 10:51.660
It's so late.

10:51.680 --> 10:53.040
They should be closed by now.

10:53.040 --> 10:54.690
Are police stations ever closed?

10:54.690 --> 10:57.690
Are you worried you won't be able
to check into a hotel?

10:57.760 --> 11:00.120
I know
there are a few small motels nearby.

11:00.600 --> 11:02.440
Although the environment is a bit poor,

11:02.440 --> 11:04.080
you could make do for one night.

11:04.080 --> 11:05.740
You really can make things up.

11:05.780 --> 11:09.040
Do you think I don't know
small motels require ID cards too?

11:09.260 --> 11:10.770
I just don't know

11:10.800 --> 11:13.370
if you're afraid of mice or cockroaches.

11:16.320 --> 11:17.360
Childish.

11:18.440 --> 11:19.730
There's another way.

11:19.760 --> 11:21.290
If you don't mind,

11:21.320 --> 11:22.600
I actually have a spare room at my place.

11:22.600 --> 11:23.630
It's a deal.

11:25.790 --> 11:27.200
It went so smoothly?

11:37.640 --> 11:38.600
Sorry about this.

11:38.600 --> 11:39.870
I only have

11:39.870 --> 11:42.240
-pink wool slippers.
-What does she mean?

11:42.630 --> 11:44.030
Is this a psychological trick?

11:44.030 --> 11:46.390
Actually, I don't mind if you go barefoot.

11:46.390 --> 11:47.200
I do.

11:48.080 --> 11:49.660
He's even okay with this?

11:49.690 --> 11:51.890
Ms. Lin, what do you usually do at night?

11:52.240 --> 11:53.200
Read books or surf the internet?

11:53.200 --> 11:54.920
Not picky at all.

11:54.950 --> 11:55.900
Both.

11:57.010 --> 11:58.020
[The Philosophy of History]

11:58.940 --> 12:01.360
To be able to read
an original book like this,

12:01.360 --> 12:02.890
you must be a professional.

12:03.670 --> 12:04.870
I used to be.

12:04.870 --> 12:05.960
None of your business.

12:05.960 --> 12:06.600
What about now?

12:06.600 --> 12:08.670
Now, I'm a proud

12:08.670 --> 12:10.910
Sports Equipment Keeper.

12:13.720 --> 12:16.000
Very vigilant.

12:23.440 --> 12:24.960
Oh no, his ID card.

12:24.960 --> 12:27.270
Look, those are my collected blind boxes.

12:27.270 --> 12:30.030
-Aren't they cute?
-What doesn't she want me to see?

12:30.030 --> 12:31.230
Take a seat anywhere.

12:43.700 --> 12:45.610
He's such a big guy.

12:45.630 --> 12:47.110
Your home

12:47.130 --> 12:48.200
is really crowded.

12:48.300 --> 12:49.230
Crowded?

12:50.000 --> 12:51.550
I think it's very scientific.

12:51.550 --> 12:52.280
Scientific?

12:53.320 --> 12:55.750
Everything is on the line of action.

12:55.750 --> 12:56.950
Isn't it scientific?

12:57.440 --> 12:59.190
I have to find a chance
to check her computer.

12:59.190 --> 13:01.590
I let you sit,
and you're still being picky.

13:01.840 --> 13:02.630
How about

13:02.630 --> 13:03.680
you sit on the sofa?

13:03.680 --> 13:04.940
I'll tidy it up for you.

13:05.790 --> 13:06.790
Are you hungry?

13:06.790 --> 13:08.030
How about I order some takeout for you?

13:08.030 --> 13:09.270
How about a burger?

13:09.270 --> 13:10.400
I don't eat takeout.

13:10.840 --> 13:12.200
Do you have any ingredients at home?

13:12.200 --> 13:12.900
Yes.

13:13.030 --> 13:13.810
In the fridge.

13:13.810 --> 13:14.940
Go see for yourself.

13:23.630 --> 13:25.960
How long have these been here?

13:25.960 --> 13:27.790
I'll just have a burger.

13:33.270 --> 13:34.240
Computer.

13:35.180 --> 13:36.510
I need to find a way to distract her.

13:36.510 --> 13:37.910
This tastes really good.

13:38.670 --> 13:39.320
Thank you.

13:39.630 --> 13:40.560
You're welcome.

13:44.240 --> 13:47.270
The Wang Fa's Strategic Plan
officially starts.

13:56.360 --> 13:57.270
You're quite the actor.

13:57.270 --> 13:58.200
I can't reach it.

13:58.840 --> 14:00.150
Why is it crooked?

14:01.790 --> 14:02.510
Fine then,

14:03.080 --> 14:04.480
I'll play along with you.

14:05.720 --> 14:08.120
This heartless guy.

14:09.680 --> 14:10.410
Hello?

14:10.440 --> 14:11.630
The food delivery is here, right?

14:11.630 --> 14:12.270
I...

14:12.790 --> 14:14.410
My stomach hurts a little.

14:14.440 --> 14:16.040
Hey,

14:16.060 --> 14:17.390
you might have to wait a moment.

14:17.390 --> 14:18.870
I'm a bit slow.

14:18.870 --> 14:20.960
Playing new tricks again.

14:23.850 --> 14:25.050
Suddenly got cramps.

14:25.140 --> 14:27.660
This guy is acting too?

14:28.240 --> 14:29.510
Exaggerated.

14:30.100 --> 14:31.500
I'll go get the delivery.

14:37.810 --> 14:39.880
[Foot-in-the-door effect]

14:58.670 --> 15:00.200
The ID is wrong,

15:00.290 --> 15:01.590
and so is the account.

15:10.620 --> 15:11.740
No more cramps?

15:11.840 --> 15:12.790
Rested enough.

15:17.370 --> 15:18.700
You can have the burger.

15:22.790 --> 15:23.910
So boring.

15:23.910 --> 15:25.240
Let's watch a movie.

15:28.200 --> 15:28.880
Okay.

15:36.510 --> 15:38.680
Watching a horror movie
in the middle of the night.

15:38.680 --> 15:40.370
What is she up to now?

15:42.390 --> 15:44.220
So scary.

15:45.290 --> 15:47.170
Aren't you scared?

15:50.990 --> 15:53.410
Then sorry, Wang.

15:53.490 --> 15:55.330
Don't blame me.

15:57.870 --> 15:59.630
Trying to scare me?

16:02.820 --> 16:04.370
Boring.

16:05.200 --> 16:07.130
Ms. Lin, is there something wrong?

16:08.950 --> 16:10.160
Nothing.

16:10.180 --> 16:11.420
Just wanted to ask

16:11.450 --> 16:12.980
what kind of drink you want.

16:14.780 --> 16:16.190
Water is fine.

16:16.220 --> 16:17.100
Thanks.

16:20.280 --> 16:23.040
Playing mind games with me?

16:23.080 --> 16:24.890
You are still too green.

16:28.190 --> 16:30.020
I still have plan B.

16:36.150 --> 16:37.060
Follow me.

17:01.290 --> 17:02.870
This is my grandparents' room.

17:02.870 --> 17:04.599
It's quite spacious, isn't it?

17:09.000 --> 17:11.060
You can make do here for tonight.

17:12.510 --> 17:13.270
Thank you.

17:19.720 --> 17:21.550
Finally, some peace and quiet.

17:26.440 --> 17:28.640
No matter how hard it is,
it won't be hard for me.

17:28.640 --> 17:30.400
I don't believe this.

17:36.050 --> 17:39.330
You short-circuited
the house last time, right?

17:45.640 --> 17:47.130
Again?

17:47.620 --> 17:50.140
Ms. Lin has so much energy.

17:58.500 --> 17:59.700
Coach Wang?

18:06.030 --> 18:06.790
Coach Wang?

18:11.240 --> 18:12.110
Coach Wang?

18:15.790 --> 18:16.510
I'm sorry.

18:16.510 --> 18:17.770
The power shorted out.

18:17.880 --> 18:19.740
Old buildings are just like this.

18:20.830 --> 18:22.560
I'm a little afraid of the dark.

18:22.590 --> 18:24.160
If you don't mind,

18:24.160 --> 18:25.220
let's have a drink.

18:25.590 --> 18:27.920
Really full of tricks.

18:43.200 --> 18:45.850
Alright, I'm not playing along anymore.

18:47.970 --> 18:49.850
Ms. Lin, you seem to really like

18:49.880 --> 18:51.640
using psychological tricks.

18:52.640 --> 18:53.540
For example,

18:53.570 --> 18:55.060
the foot-in-the-door effect.

18:55.060 --> 18:56.500
First, you asked me to do

18:56.550 --> 18:57.850
some boring things,

18:57.870 --> 18:59.710
then you made your real request.

19:00.460 --> 19:01.870
What is this one called?

19:01.890 --> 19:03.630
Is it called the suspension bridge effect?

19:03.630 --> 19:05.200
The horror movie is just a setup.

19:05.200 --> 19:07.000
The power outage in the old house
is the main event.

19:07.000 --> 19:08.750
Once we finish our beers

19:08.750 --> 19:09.790
in the dark of the blackout,

19:09.790 --> 19:10.830
we'll become comrades who crossed

19:10.830 --> 19:12.690
the suspension bridge together.

19:14.420 --> 19:15.140
Right?

19:17.180 --> 19:18.470
Coach Wang,

19:19.310 --> 19:21.700
you're really overthinking this.

19:25.000 --> 19:26.000
I hope so.

19:27.020 --> 19:28.680
But let me make it clear first:

19:29.170 --> 19:30.580
I won't be their coach.

19:32.120 --> 19:33.640
All for nothing.

19:36.350 --> 19:37.830
I'm suddenly a bit sleepy.

19:39.320 --> 19:41.260
[Suspension bridge effect]

19:43.160 --> 19:44.640
Playing games with me?

19:50.330 --> 19:53.410
I guess I have to fix
the power outage I caused.

19:58.680 --> 20:00.700
The circuit breaker probably burned out.

20:00.700 --> 20:02.150
Why is he here?

20:02.180 --> 20:03.280
It's too late now.

20:03.310 --> 20:05.170
Let's call a repairman tomorrow.

20:06.820 --> 20:07.620
Wait a minute.

20:12.490 --> 20:13.250
Thanks.

20:47.260 --> 20:48.550
The circuit breaker has been replaced.

20:48.550 --> 20:50.150
The pipes will be fixed today.

20:50.150 --> 20:52.480
Thank you for taking me in, Miss Landlady.

21:00.750 --> 21:03.210
He's even harder
to deal with than I thought.

21:03.440 --> 21:04.720
But...

21:04.940 --> 21:06.660
I have my ways.

21:07.520 --> 21:11.180
[Door-in-the-face effect:
Excessive requests, fallback demands]

21:07.840 --> 21:09.860
Strategy No. 3,

21:10.440 --> 21:12.160
the door-in-the-face effect.

21:12.160 --> 21:14.400
When you want to open the skylight,

21:14.430 --> 21:16.640
you can ask to remove the roof first.

21:16.720 --> 21:19.030
Under extreme shock,

21:19.030 --> 21:21.490
the request for a skylight
will be accepted.

21:21.760 --> 21:23.410
Door-in-the-face effect.

21:24.790 --> 21:26.550
Could it be too extreme?

21:31.970 --> 21:32.720
[Director Qian]

21:34.270 --> 21:36.720
Director Qian is putting pressure
on me again.

21:36.720 --> 21:38.480
Better you than me.

21:38.480 --> 21:39.920
Sorry, Wang Fa.

21:39.920 --> 21:41.750
Time to cross the Rubicon.

21:42.750 --> 21:43.960
I can only bet on this.

21:59.590 --> 22:01.470
I came because I just used
the water upstairs.

22:01.470 --> 22:03.030
Has it affected you?

22:03.950 --> 22:04.760
Everything is normal.

22:04.760 --> 22:05.610
No leaks.

22:05.740 --> 22:06.610
Good.

22:09.860 --> 22:10.820
Wait.

22:12.640 --> 22:15.680
I have a very sincere request.

22:15.700 --> 22:16.790
I told you.

22:17.510 --> 22:19.170
I don't want to be their coach.

22:20.410 --> 22:22.100
Then be my boyfriend.

22:24.640 --> 22:26.350
Is it that scary?

22:31.110 --> 22:33.370
These cookies represent my love for you.

22:37.440 --> 22:39.170
The door-in-the-face effect.

22:40.670 --> 22:42.020
First make a request

22:42.040 --> 22:44.130
that the other person
can't possibly accept,

22:44.130 --> 22:45.660
then lower the difficulty,

22:45.680 --> 22:46.940
and then make a request

22:47.000 --> 22:48.930
that is relatively easy to accept.

22:52.190 --> 22:54.540
You did your research.

22:54.780 --> 22:56.380
So, Ms. Lin, you think

22:57.140 --> 22:58.660
that being your boyfriend

22:58.940 --> 23:00.740
is harder for me to accept

23:00.760 --> 23:03.020
than being their football coach, right?

23:03.550 --> 23:04.620
Isn't it?

23:17.670 --> 23:18.700
Not necessarily.

23:21.130 --> 23:22.660
In terms of shamelessness,

23:22.780 --> 23:24.500
I really lost.

23:28.540 --> 23:29.610
Anything else,

23:30.350 --> 23:31.240
Ms. Lin?

23:32.680 --> 23:33.750
It's your specialty

23:33.750 --> 23:34.790
and you're good at it.

23:34.790 --> 23:37.250
What's wrong with earning
some extra money?

23:38.200 --> 23:39.550
Football is not a game.

23:39.880 --> 23:41.310
It's not as simple as you think.

23:41.310 --> 23:42.810
I don't understand football,

23:42.810 --> 23:45.370
but the kids of the Hongjing team do.

23:46.510 --> 23:48.400
They really need a professional coach.

23:48.400 --> 23:49.640
Because they need it,

23:49.710 --> 23:51.170
others should sacrifice?

23:51.790 --> 23:53.200
You can think about it again.

23:53.200 --> 23:54.330
You just don't know them.

23:54.330 --> 23:55.330
Do you?

23:56.670 --> 23:57.400
I...

24:01.000 --> 24:02.460
Why do they play football?

24:03.880 --> 24:05.740
What formations are they good at?

24:06.820 --> 24:08.200
What are their strengths

24:08.200 --> 24:09.370
and weaknesses?

24:10.070 --> 24:11.400
Do you know everything?

24:14.390 --> 24:16.190
What does football mean to them?

24:16.390 --> 24:17.220
An interest,

24:17.420 --> 24:18.310
a hobby,

24:18.330 --> 24:19.590
or their whole future?

24:22.850 --> 24:25.020
You don't even know any of these,

24:26.030 --> 24:28.200
yet you talk to me about their needs.

24:30.890 --> 24:32.820
When I was a coach in Nanton before,

24:33.130 --> 24:34.190
not to exaggerate,

24:34.950 --> 24:36.000
the youth team I coached

24:36.000 --> 24:38.240
was full of gifted boys.

24:39.130 --> 24:41.000
I'm not suitable

24:41.020 --> 24:42.280
for the Hongjing team,

24:42.590 --> 24:43.920
and I am not interested.

24:54.350 --> 24:55.680
Do you understand them?

24:56.620 --> 24:58.080
Why do they play football?

24:58.230 --> 25:00.090
What formations are they good at?

25:00.440 --> 25:01.640
What are their strengths

25:01.640 --> 25:02.680
and weaknesses?

25:04.070 --> 25:05.870
What does football mean to them?

25:05.970 --> 25:06.900
An interest,

25:06.930 --> 25:07.820
a hobby,

25:07.910 --> 25:09.260
or their whole future?

25:09.980 --> 25:12.000
You don't even know any of these,

25:12.550 --> 25:15.110
yet you talk to me about their needs.

25:27.910 --> 25:29.350
When I took the time to learn about

25:29.350 --> 25:31.170
these kids' pasts,

25:31.200 --> 25:32.920
my heart

25:32.940 --> 25:34.870
couldn't calm down for a long time.

25:39.030 --> 25:42.810
[Report on the Recruitment
of the Football Intensive Training Class]

25:39.110 --> 25:42.270
Report on the Recruitment
of the Football Intensive Training Class.

25:42.270 --> 25:44.920
The Education Committee
of Hongjing No. 8 High School has decided

25:44.920 --> 25:46.810
to establish a football team.

25:46.830 --> 25:47.830
Fu Xinshu, Qi Liang.

25:47.830 --> 25:51.270
Report on the Disbandment
of the Football Intensive Training Class.

25:48.420 --> 25:55.700
[Report on the Disbandment
of the Football Intensive Training Class]

25:51.880 --> 25:54.200
Coach Jiang of the football team resigned.

25:54.200 --> 25:56.460
The Education Committee has decided...

26:01.360 --> 26:03.260
[Spade Q, Lin Wanxing]

26:13.050 --> 26:14.540
[British overseas student,
majoring in Psychology]

26:14.540 --> 26:15.450
[Loves spicy food, hates coriander]

26:15.480 --> 26:16.260
[Bad at sports, can't ride a bike]

26:17.240 --> 26:18.800
Lin Wanxing,

26:19.040 --> 26:21.910
I must know if you are the Spade Q.

26:31.980 --> 26:33.640
You really entered her house?

26:35.160 --> 26:35.990
And then what?

26:38.030 --> 26:39.250
I secretly checked her QQ.

26:39.250 --> 26:40.030
Did you find anything?

26:40.030 --> 26:41.110
Is she the Spade Q?

26:41.950 --> 26:43.210
The name is different.

26:45.300 --> 26:46.760
So what are you going to do?

26:50.600 --> 26:51.850
Look for another chance

26:51.850 --> 26:53.110
to observe her further.

26:53.110 --> 26:54.770
What do you mean by "further"?

26:55.590 --> 26:57.190
Break the water pipes again?

26:58.110 --> 26:59.400
And live in her house?

27:00.390 --> 27:03.160
[Lin Wanxing]

27:11.580 --> 27:12.060
[Lin Wanxing]

27:16.370 --> 27:17.370
Coach Wang,

27:17.480 --> 27:19.540
a box of books needs moving at school.

27:20.070 --> 27:20.870
Don't hang up.

27:22.160 --> 27:23.110
You'll be paid.

27:23.920 --> 27:25.030
You name the price.

27:37.160 --> 27:38.290
Where are the books?

27:39.000 --> 27:39.850
Follow me.

27:45.050 --> 27:50.690
[Class 12, Grade 10]

27:53.520 --> 28:03.280
[Class 12, Grade 10]

27:56.640 --> 27:58.370
Isn't this an empty classroom?

27:59.110 --> 28:00.720
Except for substitute Chen Weidong,

28:00.720 --> 28:01.880
the team members were specially recruited

28:01.880 --> 28:03.680
into Hongjing No. 8 High School.

28:03.750 --> 28:04.510
Here

28:04.920 --> 28:06.880
used to be Class 12, Grade 10,

28:06.910 --> 28:08.510
the Sports Specialty Class.

28:08.680 --> 28:10.680
Since middle school,
they've been teammates

28:10.680 --> 28:11.960
and classmates.

28:12.550 --> 28:13.440
They studied

28:13.440 --> 28:14.720
and trained together.

28:14.590 --> 28:18.270
[Class 12, Grade 10,
Hongjing No. 8 High School]

28:14.740 --> 28:15.940
They were very close.

28:18.750 --> 28:20.090
-Coming!
-Come on.

28:20.480 --> 28:21.480
Feng Suo, come on.

28:32.240 --> 28:33.480
Once more. Once more.

28:37.920 --> 28:39.170
Later,

28:39.250 --> 28:41.270
the coach who promised
to lead the team didn't show up,

28:41.270 --> 28:43.630
and their forward transferred
to another school.

28:43.630 --> 28:46.360
The football team and the specialty class
were disbanded.

28:46.360 --> 28:49.190
They were put into different classes.

29:09.080 --> 29:13.390
[Class 5, Grade 12]

29:18.750 --> 29:19.860
No. 9 Qin Ao

29:20.000 --> 29:21.000
is an aggressive forward

29:21.000 --> 29:22.250
and the main scorer.

29:22.280 --> 29:23.680
He's very explosive.

29:24.140 --> 29:25.590
Although he is usually loud

29:25.590 --> 29:27.070
and looks careless,

29:27.070 --> 29:28.920
he actually has a high offensive awareness

29:28.920 --> 29:30.790
and is good at dribbling past defenders.

29:30.790 --> 29:32.640
The one next to him is Lin Lu,

29:32.640 --> 29:33.690
a center-back.

29:33.720 --> 29:35.190
He is

29:35.210 --> 29:37.010
the smallest in the team,

29:37.040 --> 29:38.160
but very agile.

29:45.840 --> 29:47.510
The curly-haired guy
they're always messing with

29:47.510 --> 29:48.440
is Yu Ming.

29:48.440 --> 29:49.440
He's a left-back.

29:50.240 --> 29:51.350
He's very well-behaved.

29:51.350 --> 29:53.390
He can firmly execute assigned tactics.

29:53.390 --> 29:54.920
He's absolutely reliable.

30:04.200 --> 30:05.000
Ms. Lin?

30:08.000 --> 30:09.260
What is she doing here?

30:10.240 --> 30:11.500
Looking for the coach.

30:15.720 --> 30:17.510
The one doing homework is Fu Xinshu.

30:17.510 --> 30:18.750
He's our captain

30:18.750 --> 30:20.350
and the pillar of the team.

30:20.470 --> 30:21.510
He is the one

30:21.550 --> 30:23.410
most passionate about football.

30:29.200 --> 30:31.240
Hello, Ms. Lin. Hello, Coach.

30:33.200 --> 30:34.550
Go back to your homework.

30:34.550 --> 30:35.000
Okay.

30:36.680 --> 30:37.540
And over there.

30:47.520 --> 30:48.390
This way.

30:48.830 --> 30:50.230
You have 10 minutes left.

30:51.830 --> 30:53.560
How come I only have 10 minutes?

30:54.480 --> 30:57.200
Because my patience
will only last 10 more minutes.

30:57.200 --> 30:58.930
Just get straight to the point.

31:01.000 --> 31:01.680
Alright.

31:02.480 --> 31:04.070
Asking you to move books was a lie.

31:04.070 --> 31:05.390
I just hoped that you

31:05.510 --> 31:07.810
could get to know those boys properly.

31:08.440 --> 31:09.370
I've known them.

31:09.750 --> 31:10.590
So what?

31:11.440 --> 31:13.840
Maybe you'd be willing
to change your mind.

31:19.510 --> 31:21.920
Actually, those kids are quite pitiful.

31:23.480 --> 31:25.440
Except for the students
on the football team,

31:25.440 --> 31:27.620
no one else wants to play with them.

31:28.200 --> 31:29.960
They have been marginalized.

31:31.480 --> 31:32.600
Ms. Lin,

31:33.100 --> 31:35.440
what kind of psychological effect is this?

31:35.440 --> 31:36.790
Emotional blackmail?

31:37.550 --> 31:38.510
Of course not.

31:39.680 --> 31:40.750
Actually,

31:40.750 --> 31:42.000
I have a question

31:42.000 --> 31:43.790
I want to ask you, Coach Wang.

31:44.350 --> 31:46.310
Many of them say

31:46.310 --> 31:48.110
they never want to play football again.

31:48.110 --> 31:49.370
Do you think it's true?

31:51.550 --> 31:54.080
Judging from their performance
on the pitch,

31:54.350 --> 31:55.680
it doesn't seem like it.

31:57.850 --> 31:59.290
Then I was right.

32:00.440 --> 32:01.680
They were once

32:01.680 --> 32:03.080
abandoned by their coach

32:03.270 --> 32:04.510
and their teammates,

32:05.150 --> 32:07.210
and lost the chance to play football.

32:07.550 --> 32:08.640
Because they are heartbroken,

32:08.640 --> 32:10.570
they shout loudly,

32:10.750 --> 32:11.990
"To hell with football,

32:11.990 --> 32:13.510
I will never play again!"

32:15.200 --> 32:16.860
But once they get on the pitch,

32:17.310 --> 32:19.030
they still run so hard

32:19.030 --> 32:20.310
and give it their all.

32:21.790 --> 32:23.200
Even an amateur like me

32:23.590 --> 32:25.790
can tell they're not telling the truth.

32:30.700 --> 32:32.030
Don't easily

32:32.130 --> 32:34.700
fall into the self-satisfaction
of saving others,

32:34.700 --> 32:35.830
Ms. Lin.

32:42.780 --> 32:43.600
Fine.

32:43.830 --> 32:44.910
To be honest,

32:44.930 --> 32:47.120
I came to this school
to be the Sports Equipment Keeper

32:47.120 --> 32:48.460
just for an easier life.

32:49.480 --> 32:51.110
I hope you can come and be the coach

32:51.110 --> 32:52.400
for the same reason.

32:52.790 --> 32:53.830
If you can,

32:53.890 --> 32:55.520
you can ease my burden

32:55.550 --> 32:56.710
and save my job.

32:59.340 --> 33:00.530
In human communication,

33:00.530 --> 33:02.460
sincerity is the ultimate weapon.

33:02.550 --> 33:03.440
I admit

33:03.640 --> 33:05.510
I did use
some psychological effects earlier

33:05.510 --> 33:06.840
to try and persuade you.

33:11.900 --> 33:13.200
This ID card

33:13.400 --> 33:14.530
was also taken by me.

33:14.910 --> 33:15.840
[Name: Wang Fa]

33:16.130 --> 33:16.960
Here you go.

33:25.310 --> 33:26.910
My actions were calculated,

33:30.440 --> 33:32.310
but my desire for you to be the coach

33:32.310 --> 33:33.310
is sincere.

33:37.510 --> 33:38.600
Coach Wang Fa,

33:39.510 --> 33:41.240
I sincerely beg you once again

33:41.240 --> 33:42.960
to become the team's coach.

33:43.510 --> 33:44.480
Help them

33:45.400 --> 33:46.400
and help me.

33:49.950 --> 33:51.610
What do you mean by "further"?

33:52.090 --> 33:53.690
Break the water pipes again?

33:54.720 --> 33:56.310
And move into her house?

34:01.750 --> 34:03.880
I think you're starting to win me over.

34:05.200 --> 34:05.960
Really?

34:06.550 --> 34:07.810
But I have a condition.

34:08.239 --> 34:09.070
What is it?

34:11.960 --> 34:12.889
Let's make a bet.

34:15.550 --> 34:17.949
You experience my disciplined lifestyle.

34:17.949 --> 34:19.449
If you can stick to it,

34:19.880 --> 34:20.880
I might agree.

34:21.320 --> 34:22.110
No...

34:23.320 --> 34:24.510
But since it's a bet,

34:24.880 --> 34:26.590
shouldn't you also join in

34:26.590 --> 34:28.250
and experience my lifestyle?

34:29.400 --> 34:30.750
Whoever can't endure it

34:30.780 --> 34:32.060
loses.

34:34.070 --> 34:34.920
Deal.

35:01.160 --> 35:02.260
[Good morning]

35:03.300 --> 35:05.260
It's the weekend today.

35:10.730 --> 35:12.250
Who is it?

35:25.190 --> 35:26.360
Coach Wang,

35:26.990 --> 35:29.240
do you know what time it is?

35:29.270 --> 35:31.430
Who agreed to swap lives yesterday?

35:32.450 --> 35:35.180
But it's too early.

35:37.070 --> 35:37.930
It's not early.

35:38.440 --> 35:39.630
Usually at this time,

35:39.630 --> 35:41.690
I've already started my morning run.

35:41.710 --> 35:43.760
Bro, are you even human?

35:43.760 --> 35:45.800
How about this? Let's set the rules first.

35:45.800 --> 35:47.110
There are rules?

35:48.190 --> 35:49.990
Why didn't you say so yesterday?

35:50.280 --> 35:51.760
Speechless.

35:53.060 --> 35:54.600
[Time] [Training Schedule]
[Key Objectives] [Remarks]

35:54.420 --> 35:55.890
Fasted cardio.

35:54.620 --> 35:56.460
[Wake Up & Warm-up Activation]
[Fasted Cardio Session]

35:58.400 --> 35:59.770
6 a.m.

35:59.680 --> 36:01.700
[Indoor Cardio Training] [Dinner Time]
[Evening Cardio]

36:00.440 --> 36:01.880
Evening cardio.

36:02.630 --> 36:03.760
Coach,

36:04.550 --> 36:07.510
your schedule
is stricter than military training.

36:09.090 --> 36:10.530
This is how I usually am.

36:12.640 --> 36:14.490
This is how I usually am.

36:15.190 --> 36:16.960
Double-digit step count.

36:16.960 --> 36:18.670
Lazing around all afternoon on weekends.

36:18.670 --> 36:19.800
Can you do that?

36:20.850 --> 36:23.040
I've never seen anyone so lazy.

36:24.380 --> 36:25.380
I can.

36:27.880 --> 36:29.760
Then...

36:29.780 --> 36:32.820
eating river snail rice noodles barefoot,

36:33.830 --> 36:36.930
and doing handstands in a lace slip dress
while eating spicy wheat gluten snacks.

36:36.930 --> 36:38.060
You can do those too?

36:38.380 --> 36:40.320
You're pushing your luck.

36:43.320 --> 36:45.590
Your usual hobbies

36:45.620 --> 36:46.910
are quite unique.

36:46.960 --> 36:47.990
So,

36:48.010 --> 36:50.140
you see, you can't accept them either.

36:50.190 --> 36:52.840
Swapping lives requires
reasonable requests.

36:52.840 --> 36:55.190
The fasted cardio,

36:55.130 --> 36:56.880
[Indoor Cardio Training] [Dinner Time]
[Evening Cardio]

36:55.190 --> 36:57.190
physical training,

36:57.210 --> 37:00.480
and night jogging should all be deleted.

37:02.890 --> 37:04.250
Let's compromise.

37:04.540 --> 37:05.520
In the morning,

37:05.830 --> 37:07.430
you follow my arrangements.

37:07.630 --> 37:08.710
Reasonable,

37:08.920 --> 37:10.320
not strict ones.

37:14.110 --> 37:15.000
And in the afternoon?

37:15.000 --> 37:16.000
In the afternoon,

37:16.880 --> 37:17.940
I'll listen to you.

37:20.960 --> 37:22.000
Deal.

37:35.740 --> 37:37.150
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

37:37.930 --> 37:39.420
♪ Because you're with me ♪

37:42.160 --> 37:43.690
♪ The light shimmers ♪

37:44.950 --> 37:46.190
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

37:47.880 --> 37:49.030
♪ Running towards you ♪
